on Zacks.com





Alibaba, Weibo, Sina Aren't The Only Breakout China Stocks; Here's Another
Unless you've been living under one of the rocks in the Great Wall of China, you've noticed that Chinese internet stocks like Alibaba (BABA), Weibo (WB) and Sina (SINA) have been on the rise recently. Internet portal Sohu.com (SOHU) has also joined the rally. Sohu broke out last week and picked up another upgrade to its Relative Strength (RS) Rating on Friday, from 80 to 83 Friday. IBD's proprietary RS Rating identifies technical performance by

