Sohu.com Inc.


            
            Sohu.com, Inc. is a holding company, which engages in the development and provision of online media, gaming, and mobile applications. It operates through the following segments: Sohu, Sogou, and Changyou. The company was founded by Charles Zhang in August 1996 and is headquartered in Beijing, China.

            
